original_title: The Warwick Rowers - WR17 Spain Film
overview: A beautifully crafted documentary that takes you behind the scenes of our 2017 calendar shoots in Spain.  Shot on location in Spain in glorious colour and full 4k definition, available as a download only.  The Warwick Rowers are back for 2017 to raise money for charity.
title: The Warwick Rowers - WR17 Spain Film
